  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manifest acidic chakra in the form of two whips of acid designed to grapple and melt into your foes.</p><p>Make two ranged ninjutsu attack, dealing 2d6 acid damage on a hit. Additionally, creature you hit must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, they become grappled by you and your acid whips for the duration. A creature grappled by your acid whips takes 1d6 acid damage at the beginning of each of their turns.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of attacks you make by +1.</p>",
